     <h1>welcome to <br>human resources!</h1> 
     <p>Welcome to the Human Resources Department at Westmont College. Whether you are a job applicant, new or existing employee, or a manager, we hope you will find helpful information at this website. </p> 
     <p>Our goal is to provide you with accurate, timely, and valuable information, services, and resources to support you in your work at Westmont. Please select the category that best suits your interest to locate information relating to current openings, employment, benefits, and a wide range of other services and resources. <br> </p> 
     <h3 align="left"><a href="./#WorkingatWestmont.html">Applicants</a></h3> 
     <p>Discover the right<a href="./#staff-openings.html"> career opportunity for you</a>! Applicants for employment with Westmont College will find our current openings and reasons to <a href="./#WorkingatWestmont.html">Work at Westmont</a> by following the links.</p> 
     <h3><a href="./#NewHires.html">New Employees</a></h3> 
     <p>Are you a new employee at Westmont College? Information at our <a href="./#NewHires.html">New Hire Website</a> will help you get off to a great start. </p> 
     <h3><a href="./#NewHires.html">Current Employees</a></h3> 
     <p>Are you a current employee at Westmont College? Information is available on our website explains <a href="./#BenefitsataGlance.html"> your benefits</a>, provides access the <a href="on_campus/handbook_new/toc">Employee Handbook</a>, and connect you with <a href="./#WellnessInformation.html">Wellness Program </a>and other resources.</p> 
     <h3><a href="on_campus/supervisor-information/">Supervisors</a> </h3> 
     <p>Access useful information to help you in recruiting, hiring, retaining and developing your staff to their full potential and help you hone your own skills as a manager. <a href="on_campus/supervisor-information/">Find resources to assist you here. </a></p> 
     <p>&nbsp;</p> 
     <h2>Want to Hire a Great Student? </h2> 
     <h3><strong><a href="http://www.westmont.edu/_offices/olp/EmployersPostingPolicyPage.html">Recruit Westmont Students</a></strong></h3> 
     <ul> 
      <li><em> Partner with Westmont’s Office of Life Planning to find and hire current Westmont students and alumni.</em></li> 
     </ul> 
     <!-- InstanceEndEditable -->
